==Translingual==
===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[papilio]]'', butterfly

===Proper noun===
'''''Papilionoideae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] of a [[subfamily]], within the family ''Leguminosae''. The [[circumscription]] of this group may vary with [[taxonomic]] viewpoint. It will be the same as that of: 
:# family ''[[Papilionaceae]]'' (when this group is treated at the rank of family)
:# subfamily ''[[Faboideae]]'' in the family ''[[Fabaceae]]'' (when the name ''Fabaceae'' is used for the family, rather than ''Leguminosae'').